      <title>马里在 1.6 亿美元交易后释放了 Resolute Mining 首席执行官 Holohan</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/mali-frees-resolute-mining-ceo-holohan-after-160-million-deal</link>
